escription><pubDate>Fri, 10 Jul 2026 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.rand.org/pubs/external_publications/EP71409.html</guid></item><item><title>让健康保险更实惠：克里斯汀·艾布纳问答</title><link>https://www.rand.org/pubs/commentary/2026/07/making-health-insurance-more-affordable-qa-with-christine-eibner.html</link><description>&lt;img height="90" src="https://www.rand.org/content/rand/pubs/commentary/2026/07/making-health-insurance-more-affordable-qa-with-christine-eibner/_jcr_content/par/teaser.crop.160x90.cm.jpeg/1783690763268.jpeg" width="160" /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;p class="desc"&gt;美国高昂的医疗费用已经成为一个非常大的问题。在本次问答中，兰德公司的克里斯汀·艾布纳 (Christine Eibner) 解释了有多少美国人拥有医疗保险、削减成本的方法以及所涉及的权衡。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt; &lt;span style="font-size: 12px; color: gray;"&gt;（使用&lt;a href="https://fetchrss.com/feedLink?w=67d7ba1d141b09f2900edc32" target="_blank"&gt;FetchRSS&lt;/a&gt;生成的提要）&lt;/span&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 Jul 2026 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.rand.org/pubs/commentary/2026/07/making-health-insurance-more-affordable-qa-with-christine-eibner.html</guid></item><item><title>使用索赔数据筛选医疗保险受益人的功能限制</title><link>https://www.rand.org/pubs/external_publications/EP71401.html</link><description>&lt;p class="desc"&gt;本文描述了基于调查的功能限制指数和用于预测限制的新的基于索赔的模型的开发。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt; &lt;span style="font-size: 12px; color: gray;"&gt;（使用&lt;a href="https://fetchrss.com/feedLink?w=67d7ba1d141b09f2900edc32" target="_blank"&gt;FetchRSS&lt;/a&gt;生成的提要）&lt;/span&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 Jul 2026 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.rand.org/pubs/external_publications/EP71401.html</guid></item></channel></rss>